<span id="freeTextContainer9914639663166997937">This book, in my opinion, is basically Indian chick-lit. It isn&apos;t the more serious Indian fiction that I prefer. Regardless, it isn&apos;t the author&apos;s fault that I chose the wrong kind of book to read for myself. And it was entertaining and the writing was good, despite the constant eye-rolling drama and girly tears. For that reason I am rating it 3 stars.</span>
